Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢大家今晚来看我们的演出\N{\r}Thank you all for coming to see us tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}今天是科帕俱乐部的周六狂欢夜\N{\r}It's Saturday night in the Copa!
