Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们会竭尽全力确保你们玩得开心\N{\r}We're gonna do our best to make sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一如既往 我们要特别感谢朱尔斯·波德尔先生\N{\r}As always a very special thanks to Mr. Jules Podell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}朱尔斯·波德尔\N{\r}是科帕卡巴纳夜店的运营者
