Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}开始吧\N{\r}Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}*我已经完全被那古老的黑魔法控制*\N{\r}*That old black magic has me in its spell*
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}*就是你运用得如此娴熟的黑魔法*\N{\r}*That old black magic that you weave so well*
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:02:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}*那冰冷的手指顺着我的脊柱上下探索*\N{\r}*Those icy fingers up and down my spine*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}*跟我们目光相接时你施展的巫术一样*\N{\r}*The same old witchcraft when your eyes meet mine*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}*令我着迷*\N{\r}*I love them so well*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}*跟我彼时内心感受到的微微刺痛感一样*\N{\r}*The same old tingle that I feel inside*
