Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.99,0:47:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 这不是我们要用的钢琴吧 - 就是它\N{\r}- This isn't the piano, right? - That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.05,0:47:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}它不是斯坦威牌的\N{\r}It ain't a Steinway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.52,0:47:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}所以呢\N{\r}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.63,0:47:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢利医生只弹斯坦威牌的钢琴\N{\r}Dr. Shirley only plays on Steinway- brand pianos.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.24,0:47:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}合同里写好的\N{\r}It's in his written contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.56,0:47:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 谢利医生是谁 - 谢利医生...\N{\r}- Who's Dr. Shirley? - Dr. Shirley...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.23,0:47:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢利先生三重奏\N{\r}the Don Shirley Trio?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.53,0:47:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们今晚要进行演奏\N{\r}They're playing tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.14,0:47:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 这很重要吗 - 是的 对这个合同很重要\N{\r}- Does it really matter? - Yeah, it does, to this contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.82,0:47:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}算了吧兄弟 不管准备什么\N{\r}Come on man, these coons
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.80,0:47:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这些黑鬼都会照样弹\N{\r}can play on anything you put in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.88,0:47:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但这台钢琴太烂了\N{\r}But it's a piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.61,0:47:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}里面还有垃圾\N{\r}And there is garbage in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.28,0:48:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 那就把它搬出去 - 你说什么\N{\r}- So, take it out. - What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.39,0:48:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你没听错\N{\r}You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.70,0:48:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你还有两三个小时 找台干净的斯坦威钢琴来\N{\r}Hey, you got 2- 3 hours. Just get a clean Steinway in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.26,0:48:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 学校里没有斯坦威钢琴 - 这不关我事\N{\r}- There ain't no Steinway on campus. - Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.76,0:48:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我敢肯定整个印第安纳州都没有两台斯坦威钢琴\N{\r}I bet there is not two Steinways in the whole state of Indiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.80,0:48:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那你最好动作麻利点\N{\r}I guess you better move your ass then.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.91,0:48:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你以为你在跟谁说话 意大利佬\N{\r}Who do you think you're talking to, grease ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.56,0:48:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}斯坦威
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.77,0:48:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}亲爱的德洛丽丝...今天早餐我吃了牛排和鸡蛋\N{\r}Dear Dolores... This morning I had steak and eggs. For breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.18,0:49:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这个乐队一直在豪华的夜总会演出\N{\r}The band has been playing at very ritzy joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.01,0:49:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我和谢利医生相处得很好 但有时候\N{\r}Dr. Shirley and I are getting along pretty good, but sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.20,0:49:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}锡达拉皮兹市\N{\r}爱荷华州
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.16,0:49:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他会很悲伤 因此他总是买醉\N{\r}I think he gets sad and that's why he drinks too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.51,0:49:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我以前从不知道这个国家有多美\N{\r}I never knew how very beautiful this country was.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.91,0:49:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}现在亲眼看到才知道\N{\r}Now that I'm seeing it I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.39,0:49:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你不会相信大自然有多美\N{\r}You won't believe how beautiful nature is,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.68,0:49:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就像他们说的一样美\N{\r}it is as beautiful as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.37,0:49:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这边的交通情况\N{\r}And the traffic out here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.44,0:49:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对我来说没什么问题\N{\r}in the country is nothing, which is fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.99,0:49:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}现在我正在一间餐厅吃意式肉丸面\N{\r}Right now I'm eating spaghetti and meatballs
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.07,0:49:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这吃起来就像中式面条上的番茄酱一样\N{\r}in a diner that tastes like ketchup on Chinese noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.93,0:49:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们现在要南下... 到了南方后\N{\r}We are heading down south now... I will write you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.42,0:49:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我会再给你写一封信 我爱你\N{\r}another letter when we get down south. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.26,0:49:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你的丈夫托尼 替我亲亲孩子们\N{\r}Your husband Tony. P.S. Kiss the kids for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.81,0:49:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}欢迎来到肯塔基州
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.75,0:49:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你有家人吗 医生\N{\r}You got any family, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.53,0:49:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 算不上有 - 算不上有吗\N{\r}- Not really. - Not really?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.69,0:49:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要么有 要么没有\N{\r}Either you do or you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.97,0:49:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说来话长 托尼\N{\r}It's a long story, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.21,0:50:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}怎么 我们现在很赶时间吗\N{\r}What, we're in a hurry now?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.97,0:50:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}说说看吧\N{\r}Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.35,0:50:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我有个弟弟\N{\r}I have a brother somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.44,0:50:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们以前经常聚在一起...\N{\r}We used to get together once in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.27,0:50:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但后来越来越难保持联系\N{\r}but it got more and more difficult to stay in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.66,0:50:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这大概是做音乐家的诅咒吧\N{\r}Curse of being a musician I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.71,0:50:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}总是四处奔波\N{\r}Always on the road
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.02,0:50:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就像狂欢节工作者一样\N{\r}like a carnival worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.77,0:50:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}或是罪犯\N{\r}Or a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.91,0:50:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我的婚姻也受到了很大的影响\N{\r}Took quite a toll on my marriage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.42,0:50:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你结婚了吗 - 结过\N{\r}- You're married? - Was.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.49,0:50:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}她叫琼 是个好人\N{\r}June, good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.37,0:50:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}语法很糟糕 但很善良\N{\r}Terrible grammar, but a kind soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.68,0:50:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 你会很喜欢她的 - 琼吗\N{\r}- You'll quite like her. - June?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.36,0:50:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就像莱西的妈妈一样吗\N{\r}Like uh, like Lessie's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.69,0:50:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不幸的是 我没能做好\N{\r}Unfortunately, I couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.20,0:50:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一个丈夫和一个音乐会钢琴演奏家\N{\r}do a husband act and a concert pianist act.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.10,0:50:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我似乎不能兼顾这两个角色\N{\r}Couldn't seem to manage both worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.66,0:50:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}前方一千六百米处\N{\r}肯德基
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.04,0:50:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}肯德基\N{\r}Kentucky Fried Chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.84,0:50:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就在肯塔基州 你说巧不巧\N{\r}In Kentucky! When's that ever gonna happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.62,0:51:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}肯德基\N{\r}一美元 如此美味
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.04,0:51:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}肯德基\N{\r}即刻享受或打包回家
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.73,0:51:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好吧\N{\r}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.66,0:51:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你要吃什么吗\N{\r}Hey, you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.94,0:51:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不用了 谢谢你 托尼\N{\r}I'm fine. Thank you Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.37,0:51:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我觉得这是我吃过最好吃的肯德基\N{\r}I think this is the best Kentucky Fried Chicken I ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.15,0:51:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我猜这里的更新鲜 对吧\N{\r}But I guess it's fresher down here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.07,0:51:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我从没见过像你这么有胃口的人\N{\r}I don't think I've ever met anyone with your appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.49,0:51:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 我买了一桶 你可以尝尝\N{\r}No, I've bought the bucket so you could have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.21,0:51:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我这辈子从没吃过炸鸡\N{\r}I've never had fried chicken in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.59,0:51:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你在胡说什么 你们黑人很喜欢\N{\r}Who you bullshittin'? You people love
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.64,0:51:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}炸鸡 粗燕麦粉 五颜六色的蔬菜\N{\r}the fried chicken, the grits, the colored greens
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.36,0:51:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我也很喜欢\N{\r}I love it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.47,0:51:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我在军队的时候 黑人厨师总是做这些吃的\N{\r}The negro cooks used to make it all time when I was in the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.58,0:51:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你对我的评价很狭隘 托尼\N{\r}You have a very narrow assessment of me, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.39,0:51:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}对吧 我很厉害\N{\r}Yeah right? I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.61,0:51:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 你不是厉害 是糟糕\N{\r}No, you're not good, you're bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.56,0:51:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我的意思是 别的黑人\N{\r}I'm saying, just because
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.92,0:51:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}喜欢听某种类型的音乐\N{\r}other Negros enjoy certain types of music,
