Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.53,1:39:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我告诉你\N{\r}I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.99,1:39:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}那是因为天才还远远不够\N{\r}Because genius is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.03,1:39:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}要想改变人心 需要的是勇气\N{\r}It takes courage to change people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.02,1:39:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢\N{\r}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.40,1:39:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢谢\N{\r}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.87,1:40:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 晚上好 - 需要帮忙吗\N{\r}- Good evening. - Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.59,1:40:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 我理解 但是... - 怎么了\N{\r}- I understand but... - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.54,1:40:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这位先生说我不能在这里用餐\N{\r}This gentleman says that I'm not permitted dine here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.92,1:40:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 你不知道\N{\r}No, you don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.97,1:40:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他是今晚的演奏者 重头戏\N{\r}he's playing tonight, he's the main event.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.90,1:40:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}很抱歉 但这是餐厅的规矩\N{\r}I'm sorry. But it's the policy of the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.55,1:40:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 一切都还好吗 - 不 不好\N{\r}- Everything all right? - No, it's not all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.50,1:40:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这个家伙说谢利医生不能在这里用餐\N{\r}This guy is saying Dr. Shirley can't eat here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.15,1:40:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我向您道歉 但这是餐厅悠久的传统\N{\r}Well, I apologize, but these are... longstanding traditions.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.51,1:40:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}俱乐部规矩 我相信您一定理解\N{\r}Club rules. I'm sure you understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.81,1:40:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 我不理解\N{\r}No. I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.73,1:41:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我很抱歉\N{\r}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.25,1:41:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}等等 你是说他乐队里的陪衬\N{\r}Wait a minute, are you tellin' me the bozos in his band,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.23,1:41:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}和专程到此听他演奏的人们\N{\r}and these people that came here to see him play,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.53,1:41:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}他们能在这里用餐\N{\r}they can eat here,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.95,1:41:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但演出者 今晚荣誉嘉宾却不能\N{\r}but the star of the show, the talking spot of honor, he can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.29,1:41:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}恐怕是这样\N{\r}I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.98,1:41:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但他总得吃饭 总得吃晚餐\N{\r}Well he's gotta eat, I mean he's gotta have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.76,1:41:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这样吧\N{\r}I tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.80,1:41:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不如我们送些食物到他的更衣室\N{\r}Why don't we bring something to his dressing room, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.70,1:41:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}约翰 把菜单给这位先生\N{\r}John, show him the menu.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.15,1:41:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}不 我拒绝在储藏室用餐\N{\r}No. I'm not eating in that storage room.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.60,1:41:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好吧 如果您愿意\N{\r}Okay... if you'd prefer,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.81,1:41:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这条路上有一家很不错的餐馆\N{\r}there's a very popular establishment right down the road,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.34,1:41:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}橙鸟酒吧 他们肯定愿意接待您\N{\r}the Orange Bird, they'd be happy to feed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.34,1:41:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}医生 借一步说话\N{\r}Doc, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.45,1:41:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}稍等\N{\r}One second just.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.74,1:41:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}也许那地方更好呢\N{\r}C'mon, maybe that place is better anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.01,1:41:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这里的餐包硬得像石头一样\N{\r}The dinner rolls here are like rocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.75,1:41:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们就去那吃饭 速去速回\N{\r}Let's just go over... just go and come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.44,1:41:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是最后一场演出了\N{\r}It's the last show.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.22,1:42:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}咱们善始善终 熬过今晚\N{\r}Bottom of the knife. Let's just get it over with
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.55,1:42:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}就能回家 并远离这群混蛋\N{\r}and we can go home and get away from these pricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.89,1:42:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这是菜单 今晚的鱼非常新鲜\N{\r}Ah, there you go, the fish is wonderful tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.70,1:42:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}除非让我在这里用餐 否则今晚就没有演出\N{\r}Either I eat in this room, or I'm not performing tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.92,1:42:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我能和你谈谈吗\N{\r}May I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.62,1:42:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}维兰纽瓦先生 麻烦你和谢利先生讲讲理\N{\r}Mr. Villanueva, you have to talk sense to Mr. Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.01,1:42:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}让你理解我们不是针对他个人\N{\r}Please make him understand we're not insulting him personally,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.05,1:42:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这只是这里的办事方法\N{\r}this is just the way things are done down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.92,1:42:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好吧 但他不是这里的人\N{\r}Yeah, well he's not from down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.25,1:42:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你就让他别这么固执\N{\r}Just ask him to be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.29,1:42:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我这里有四百位客人等着看今晚的演出\N{\r}I got 400 guests in there who expect to be entertained tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.87,1:42:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}谢利医生希望在这里用餐\N{\r}And Dr. Shirley expects to eat tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.36,1:43:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}为什么你不能破一次例呢\N{\r}Why can't you just make an exception this one time?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.41,1:43:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我跟你讲个故事\N{\r}Lemme tell you a story.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.97,1:43:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你听说过波士顿凯尔特人篮球俱乐部吗\N{\r}You ever hear of the Boston Celtics basketball club?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.55,1:43:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 听说过 - 那些男孩两年前\N{\r}- Yeah. - Yeah, those boys came through here
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.52,1:43:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}巡回比赛时来过这里\N{\r}a couple years ago on a barnstorming tour.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.99,1:43:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}看在他们是联赛世界冠军的份儿上\N{\r}Now, seeing as they were World Champions of the league and all,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.01,1:43:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们很兴奋能让他们在这里用餐\N{\r}we were tickled to have 'em eat here,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.75,1:43:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们热烈地欢迎了他们\N{\r}we rolled out the welcome wagon.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.13,1:43:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你知道那天晚上他们是在哪张桌子上吃的晚餐吗\N{\r}So do you know what table their big coon ate at that night?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.94,1:43:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}- 不知道 - 我也不知道\N{\r}- No. - I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.10,1:43:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但反正不是我们的桌子 废话少说\N{\r}But it wasn't one of ours. Now let's cut the bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.29,1:43:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}开个价吧\N{\r}Tell me what it's gonna take.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.93,1:43:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}一百元够不够你说服那小子演出\N{\r}Say one hundred dollars and you get your boy to play?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.91,1:43:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你觉得能买通我\N{\r}You think you can buy me?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.38,1:43:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}无意冒犯 先生\N{\r}With all due respect, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.65,1:43:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}但你如果不能被买通 也坐不到现在的位置\N{\r}but you wouldn't be in a job like this if you couldn't be bought.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.57,1:43:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}别这样 托尼\N{\r}Stop! Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.64,1:43:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}没关系\N{\r}It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.16,1:43:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}如果你希望\N{\r}I'll play.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.79,1:43:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我就照常演出\N{\r}If you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.48,1:44:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}好吧\N{\r}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.64,1:44:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我们赶紧离开这鬼地方\N{\r}Let's get the fuck outta here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.16,1:44:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}什么意思 离开这里\N{\r}What do you mean, let's get outta here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.66,1:44:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你觉得自己在干什么\N{\r}Where the hell do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.99,1:44:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}唐 别这样 你签了合同\N{\r}Don, don't do this! Now you signed a contract.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.16,1:44:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我知道你是那种遵守信用的人\N{\r}And I know you're the kind of man who honors a contract!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.35,1:44:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}康妮 比尔 一切都好起来 没关系\N{\r}Connie, Bill, everything's gonna be fine. It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.36,1:44:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你还有场演出呢 先生\N{\r}You got a show to do, mister!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.93,1:44:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}赶紧回来 现在就回来 该死的 现在\N{\r}You turn yourself around. Right now goddammit! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.45,1:44:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}这就是为什么我们不雇黑人的原因\N{\r}This is why you people don't work down here,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.42,1:44:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你们根本靠不住\N{\r}cause you're unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.51,1:44:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}听见了吗\N{\r}You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.31,1:44:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}我特地为你从亚特兰大运来一架斯坦威钢琴\N{\r}I shipped that goddamn Steinway in from Atlanta for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.81,1:44:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}托尼\N{\r}Tony.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.60,1:44:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn宋体\shad2\4a&H50&\3c&HFF8000&\4c&HFF8000&}你饿吗\N{\r}Are you hungry?
